\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf3  recovery if the injury might have been prevented by the exercise of due care on the part of the defendant after discovering and realizing the peril of the person injured. See cases cited in }{\*\bkmkstart Bookmark_I5DY16FM2D6N6Y0010000400}
